content.rendered:
The Fiennes Side chair is a subtle side chair suitable for a wide variety of settings such as hotels, bars, schools & offices.

The Fiennes is available in a variety of frame styles and wood finishes to suit your needs. The Fiennes pairs well with a wide range of our tables to complete your look! Made with a black steel 4 leg frame and an Ash shell.

Held in stock for delivery in 2-3 working days. 1 year guarantee.

Indoor use only. This item may require self assembly. Stackable 4 high.
